caption.text:
This is the reels strategy that I’m using for the next 90 days⬇️

The goal? Get followers and make money 💸 

There are 3 types of content I’m using:

1️⃣ Engagement runners 🏃 

- 7 second clips w captions 
- Short trending audios
- Niche relevant trends
- Podcast clips

The idea for this is to get new eyes on your page, new followers etc.

2️⃣ Content to Nurture🫂

- Tutorials
- Personal stories
- Memes
- Talking head videos

The idea here is to build a connection with your audience, build trust and authority.

3️⃣ Sales Content

- Client testimonials 
- Case Studies
- Sales call to action

The idea of these videos is to drive sales/spark conversations with potential clients🤝

If you need help implementing this into your own content, comment the word ‘Creator’ and we’ll get you started❤️

Follow @samhxtr for more value✅

caption.text:
The secret to going viral in 30 days explained⬇️

1️⃣ The Visual Hook

Hooks aren’t just about what you say or the sound effects you use.

A key part of keeping your viewers engaged is with the visuals you use in the first 2 seconds.

Text, graphics, film burns, transitions are all a great place to get started🤝

2️⃣ Follow the trends

Instagram will push trending sounds more. Full stop.

By following what’s trending and what you can easily take inspiration from, your engagement will see a boost.

Literally just scroll through your reels feed and see what’s popping up the most📲

3️⃣ Keep it short.

The majority of content that goes viral is one of these lengths.

7 seconds 
17 seconds 
27 seconds

IG isn’t the place for long form. Yet.

4️⃣ Provide free value

Give viewers a reason to come back to your page.

There’s no point in going viral for something dumb and retaining none of the viewers as followers.

5️⃣ Practise makes perfect

‘Rome wasn’t built in a day’
‘Your first reel will suck’

All that stuff.

Keep consistent, keep learning.

You’ll get there.

But if you want to cut your learning curve in half, comment ‘creator’ and we can get you started with CreatorX

We’ll teach you exactly what you need to do.
